{"word":"H422 - אָלָה - ʼâlâh - aw-law' - Adjure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adjure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சாபமிடு, ஆணையிடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to swear, to curse"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to swear, take an oath (before God)"},{"paragraph":"2) to curse"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to put under oath, adjure"},{"paragraph":"2) to put under a curse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>adjure</i>, that is, (usually in a bad sense) <i>imprecate: - </i>adjure, curse, swear."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H422 - אָלָה - ʼâlâh - aw-law'/422\">H422</a>, <a href=\"#/H423 - אָלָה - ʼâlâh - aw-law'/423\">H423</a>, <a href=\"#/H8381 - תַּאֲלָה - taʼălâh - tah-al-aw'/8381\">H8381</a>"}]}